page.title: 12One day in 1985_A.Roythorne
page.content:
{12.40p.m.}Returned to school for Recorders group.{1.30p.m.}Topic work on "The Normans". {3.20p.m.}Went home from school.{5.05p.m.}Had my tea (Corned beef sandwiches, pork pie, slice of flapjack and a cup of tea).{ {5.45p.m.}Walked down to Tracy's house so we could go down to Brownies together at the old Church of England school Community Centre.{6.00p.m.} Brownies started.{7.15p.m.}Brownies finished and Daddy collected me and took me home.{7.30p.m.}Had my supper and completed this list.{8.00p.m.}Had a bath and went to bed.
*The end of Thursday October 3rd.1985*
